{"tid":1887040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個咸濕仔話王卓淇 靚既同我入黎！！","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T01:11:14.000Z","uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"74455bc16ab99245831d3b8acf6cdd0c46f38433","tid":1887040,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"今屆香港小姐結果已經新鮮出爐，冠軍由15號邵珮詩奪得，而9號王卓淇奪得亞軍。不過，網民隨即起底並指，王卓淇是新移民。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，王卓淇自幼在廣州長大，父母離異，與母親王婉華感情要好，她們以婆婆年老為由，取得單程證來港，並在12年1月才獲發三粒星。<br />\n<br />\n王卓淇自幼便參加不同類型的比賽和選美，亦參加過2011年中華小姐環球大賽，但12強不入，今次成為港姐亞軍，相信可助她一圓明星夢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140831/large/1409498977_4ade.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140831%2Flarge%2F1409498977_4ade.jpg&h=546e15a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾參加由鳳凰衛視舉辦的2011中華小姐環球大賽，十二強不入<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140831/large/1409498979_faef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140831%2Flarge%2F1409498979_faef.jpg&h=17ae6e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012年，代表南商參加在解放軍外國語學院舉行的全國外語院校大學英語演講比賽<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140831/large/1409498980_2596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140831%2Flarge%2F1409498980_2596.jpg&h=7f77197a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140831/large/1409498981_fb67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140831%2Flarge%2F1409498981_fb67.jpg&h=225d3c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20140831/large/1409498982_7d96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20140831%2Flarge%2F1409498982_7d96.jpg&h=38aaed05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20140831/74700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20140831%2F74700&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5ADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=d5772768\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20140831%2F74700&h=0e635a71\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20140831/74700</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一陣支那味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b058a9d3de022ae31af12d57d98a7ab4a016373","tid":1887040,"uid":8096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"支雞"},{"pid":"45b3fb5e2314e4f3b638b62ea32ae302fb74d417","tid":1887040,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"你唔講唔知邊個黎"},{"pid":"f93a0546d2a3a48d28682127ffaf661c3e42b170","tid":1887040,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:02:58.000Z","msg":"個樣支那到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33abcbc43e18d993d7b6b724455d325a81863a36","tid":1887040,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"A cup比盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2200748213d8066a5c6dbec9ff8370b38f152b5","tid":1887040,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"幾時選出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c837cd8d64d2ebf635b4de805b542943b5a987","tid":1887040,"uid":312033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"話佢靚真係要去驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729f66f72d1d66478e5bd0e73a4e3c6d81aed8ef","tid":1887040,"uid":169071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-